Scenario: Successful JSON Serialization to a simple object (Single Quote example)
Given a JSON String ({"OperatorID":"000", "OperatorName":"Luffy"}) 
When the JSON String is converted into Employee object
Then it should throw with {NoException}
Then Employee object should have the following values:
|OperatorID|OperatorName|
|000       |Luffy       |

